data.description: A must see! This beautifully renovated contemporary ranch-style home is move-in ready! It has so much to offer its new owners including: fresh paint inside and out, all new flooring, updated kitchen and bathrooms, an oversized living room, 3 bedrooms plus a den, family room with vaulted ceiling and a cozy pellet stove plus so much more! The outdoor space offers a covered patio, a fire pit, mature trees for shade and a chicken coop. This home is set on a 0.21 acre lot in a very desirable neighborhood that is minutes from everything in town.
